## Changes:
- Frog Feeder now emit a block update when Food Mobs are being spawned
- Added "Baby" textures for all custom Mob Variants (Cat, Chicken, Cow, Pig, Wolf)
- Added Cold Yellow Cow variant (Spawns in the same biomes as Vanilla Cold variant)
- Added Warm Brown Cow variant (Spawns in the same biomes as Vanilla warm variant)
- Added Sniffer Cow variant (Spawns in Sunflower Plains & Flower Forests. Drops Torchflower/Pitcher Plant)
- Added Frozen Frog variant (Can be bred in Ice Spike Biomes. Drops Ice when eating)
- Added Goose Chicken variant (Spawns in Old Growth Spruce/Pine Taiga & Dark Forests)
- Wandering Trader Mob variants now spawn less often with a Wandering Trader
- Added Livestock Breeder Block:
    - Can be crafted from 8 Hay Blocks and a Barrel
    - When placed makes Livestock Animals (Sheeps, Pigs, Rabbits, Cows, Chickens) breed every 10 minutes
    - Emits a block update whenever breeding has started
- Changed & improved how custom sounds for Mob variants work:
    - Mob Variants with custom sounds now play them like vanilla Mobs
    - Creeper Cat variant now uses Creeper Mob sounds for some of its sounds
    - Sniffer Cow variant uses Sniffer Mob sounds
    - Creaking Wolf variant now use Creaking Mob Sounds
    - Ender Pig, Chicken, Cow variants now use a mix of Enderman & Endermite sounds
    - Skeleton Cat, Chicken, Cow, Pig, Wolf variants now use Skeleton sounds
    - Strider Chicken variant now uses Strider sounds
    - Rooster Chicken variants crowing sound is now it's natural ambient sound for adults
    - Pigeons Chicken variants cooing sound is now it's natural ambient sound for adults
    - Ostrich Chicken variants grunting sound is now it's natural ambient sound for adults
    - Duck Chicken variants quacking sound is now it's natural ambient sound for adults

## Fixes:
- Cold White Cow variant using the wrong tag list for biomes to spawn in
- Dark Brown Chicken variants spawn biomes not set correctly
- Added missing lang key for Pigeon Egg